text.tspan: Pinning apps in PolyOS 6 is easy! First off, open the app menu
and hover over the app you want to pin. Then press enter.
The submenu will pop up. Click pin.
Then a message will pop up and ask what spot do you
want to pin it at. Click on the home bar. Then the app will be pinned.
To remove a pin hover over the home bar and press enter then click
remove pins. Click on the pin you would like to remove.
